Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:05.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That child said he wanted to see the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.64,0:00:08.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I couldn't take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.45,0:00:12.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There were so many things I wanted to do for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:15.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I couldn't do a single thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:19.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even though the summer had just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:39.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:42.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:43.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:50.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:28.41,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\c&HB83D41&\pos(643,96)}Episode 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:40.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad Kirishima-san recovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:41.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:48.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, when I saw that feather, I had a strange feeling too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:53.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:55.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been spaced out ever since you woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:56.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream of when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:00.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:05.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, are you still having those dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:06.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:11.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night's dream was different from any I've had before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:15.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon was out and it was so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:18.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to fly up to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:22.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sore all over, but I kept trying to go higher and higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I heard voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:25.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Voices?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:30.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The voices of many people, trying to restrain me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:35.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They echoed in my ears, so I couldn't climb anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:38.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:38.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:41.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, be carefu–
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.24,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(471,105)\c&H56177E&}LUNA'S
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.24,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(743,106)\c&HBCB9DA&}BAR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.24,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\c&HEBCA84&\pos(753,672)}Asahi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.24,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\c&H0C0000&\pos(1069,430)}USED
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.24,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\c&H0C0000&\pos(1069,581)}BOOK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.24,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\c&H0C0000&\pos(1069,718)}STORE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:53.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great, isn't it, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:59.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how it's walking without any strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:00.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:02.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It got up! It got up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the way kids should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.14,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:12.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shouldn't you be with Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:10.76,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.16,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:17.07,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko piko pikori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:17.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she went to school to take care of the animals today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:20.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why am I talking to you like it's normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:20.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:23.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:26.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doll-san, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:31.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shake hands, shake hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:31.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:32.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:39.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what being "close" is like, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I made nothing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:51.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.23,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Munch munch munch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.23,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Chew chew chew chew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:02.15,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mumchy munchy munchy munchy munchy munchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:01.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:02.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:05.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:06.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:06.45,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:09.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa hah hoo hooey hee?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:09.93,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to say something, swallow first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:13.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:17.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamio-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:19.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:20.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:21.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:24.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you make hamburgers tomorrow too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:25.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:26.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:28.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a little pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:37.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You let go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:45.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:49.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:49.25,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:07.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to use the shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:08.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:11.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get the keys to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:16.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was the stationmaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:20.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's not working here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he find work somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:29.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a token of apology, here.
