Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:34.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:38.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the bottle I found yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:41.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is stardust,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:46.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,sand grains shaped like baby stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:48.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, is it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:49.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They rustle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:56.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can have one too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, the three of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:03.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:14.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This sand was given to me by my father, when I was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:17.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then isn't it something precious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:18.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:22.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if it's Kunisaki-san and Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:30.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Kamio-san has already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:36.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible she stayed late at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:43.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kunisaki-san, are you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:48.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:49.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:52.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are already out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the other club members?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:57.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:59.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the only member.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:03.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm club president.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:04.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a really selective club.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:06.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:19.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. This is the first time I've brought her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:26.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you're not going out of your way to be here, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:27.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:29.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:37.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted the three of us to observe the stars together,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:41.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because she seems to like you, Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:43.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:51.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She talks about you constantly when she is with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:55.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She really likes you, Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:57.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell how she feels,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:03.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because she is my other half.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:04.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Other half?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:13.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru and I have always spent our time together, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:19.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:20.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:23.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:27.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...always traveling alone, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:31.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever spent time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:36.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The happiness of spending time with someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:40.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The joy of living for someone else's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:44.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure even I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:46.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,though it was a long, long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:52.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then it's Michiru Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:58.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:01.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to walk me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not like tall girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:09.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A good figure is an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:17.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I happen to be rather proud of it myself too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:19.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Proud of it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:20.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:27.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The taller you are, the closer you are to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:31.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for walking me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:35.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful walking home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:36.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, who are you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:43.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A new member of the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:48.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:50.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:51.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:52.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:55.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I helped her with some heavy bags the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:59.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for having you go to the trouble of walking my daughter home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:01.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come on inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:02.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:09.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner is already ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:12.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tohno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:16.83,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:26.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:32.29,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12\frx350\fry356\frz3.964\pos(675,346)\c&H060607&}I'm\Ndoing my\Nhomework.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:36.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:37.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:46.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:47.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:52.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito-san, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:54.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still night now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:57.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told me you had to stay late at supplemental classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:01.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:03.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:08.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you keeping a picture diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:11.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's my choice of assignment for the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maestro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:17.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did you betray me?!
Comment: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:17.13,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids! Please watch this show in a bright room,
Comment: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:18.47,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,And make sure to sit far from the TV!
Comment: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.13,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Unedited Typesetting. I think not to include it tbh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:18.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:21.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You think you can conduct this orchestra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:22.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:23.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:25.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't conduct, who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:26.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Give the baton to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:30.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only way you'll get it is over my dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:37.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Appassionato God Fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:38.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geh! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:41.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the best part!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:50.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to play cards with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:55.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:58.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:00.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:06.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Old Maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:09.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Poker?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:13.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it something simple that doesn't require thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:16.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, let's play Memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:24.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:27.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:31.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:33.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:44.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:51.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try my hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:58.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try my hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:04.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:10.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:12.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:16.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu suddenly–
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:21.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind stepping outside for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:22.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:44.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been like this ever since she was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:48.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She becomes like that when she's about to make a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:50.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When she's about to make a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:55.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had the doctor at the clinic look at her, and I've even tried going to a larger hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:56.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:15:02.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They all said it was probably only psychological and that she'd grow out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:06.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She actually had an episode at school today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:10.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They called me at work, so I went to pick her up on my bike,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and brought her straight home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:13.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:19.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping that she'd be all right with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:24.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,since she's all right when she's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:35.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:38.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll suffer these attacks as long as I'm here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should keep my distance for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:49.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her that I'll still walk her to and from school, just like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:52.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over for dinner every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:06.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault that you weren't able to stay at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you lonely living by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:13.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm living alone, I've made quite a few friends somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have some friends too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:19.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:22.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because whenever I'm about to make a friend, I start crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone always runs away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have Haruko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:30.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:33.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not my real mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:35.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:39.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko-san is actually my aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:43.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was dumped onto her because I was such a strange kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:49.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko-san didn't want me, but I still ended up living there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:52.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I don't want to cause her trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:56.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we live our separate lives under one roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:58.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:03.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a real burden on her, and I don't want to be any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:09.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I play by myself, looking for weird juices, or playing cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:12.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:13.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:16.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:20.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:23.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:25.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:33.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi hasn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:35.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's at school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:36.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be here eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:40.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not supposed to be at school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:53.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:56.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:58.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:17:59.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:00.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an indirect kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:04.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:04.76,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about adult stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:08.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:14.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:20.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:22.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:26.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bubbles are so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:29.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're empty, just like the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:32.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:34.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:37.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:41.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try going to her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:47.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If she isn't coming, then we should go visit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:53.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go to her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:54.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:55.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:59.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:01.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to pick up Misuzu too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:05.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for walking me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:08.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I can't stay today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:10.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not eating dinner with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:11.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have somewhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:13.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:21.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I met you yesterday, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:25.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the new member of the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:25.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:29.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May I see your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:30.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has she gone somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:34.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:37.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you've got the right house?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:38.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:39.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:41.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking, right? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:44.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, skipping work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:50.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohno-san's mother has been suffering from a psychological disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:53.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been checking on her whenever I get the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's convinced that the older daughter, Minagi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is instead the younger daughter that passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:01.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's believed that for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:05.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems her condition has suddenly changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:09.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When she accepted the fact that her younger daughter was, in fact, dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:11.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she erased Minagi-san from her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:17.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In her mind, neither one of her daughters have ever existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:33.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to have a little sister, named Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A precious little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:42.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother was sad because I was closer to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:48.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The baby she was expecting was supposed to fill the hole in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:54.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could have just one dream come true, what would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:56.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.39,0:20:59.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:02.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother couldn't accept the reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:06.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so she chose to live in her dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:10.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I became a fragment of that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:16.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But last night, she saw herself in a dream having a miscarriage of Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:22.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Kirishima-sensei, that made my mother accept the reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:28.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When she saw me this morning, my mother said,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Who are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:33.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:37.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:44.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the end of my dream, which I lived in as Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:50.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My wings have forgotten how to fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:57.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because for so long I've just been pretending.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:03.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a use for wings that cannot fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:42.73,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fad(300,900)\fs51\shad2.25\pos(641,293)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.93,0:23:42.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:45.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're more suited to travel than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:47.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come with me, Tohno?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:48.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.11,0:23:52.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Things can't remain like this after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.54,0:23:57.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to show you the world;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:23:59.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the real world, not a dream world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.14,0:24:07.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything started with my sin...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.83,0:24:20.14,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,0)\fs39\fscx100\fscy100\shad2.4\c&HFEFEFA&\4c&H121213&\pos(956,419)}Episode 6
